Class TCPPacketMessage

java.lang.Object
  org.happy.artist.rmdmia.rcsm.providers.ros.client.transport.tcpros.data.TCPPacketMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
TCPMessage
public class TCPPacketMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements TCPMessage

TCPPacketMessage.java is a single packet message Object implementation for TCPROS Transport protocol. This entire class is overkill for a single packet message, however, implementing for sake of usability. Personal implementation will be byte[] passing on single packet message.
